                  everything is a nail. During my first startup, we started doing too much and ended up doing
                  nothing at all. We wrote code for six months, but never released a product. I learnt that
                  I need to figure out the one thing I need to build, and build it first.
              %li
                %p
                  %strong Working in Isolation
                  %br/
